{
  "name": "RPlog_A_Blast_from_the_Past",
  "title": "A Blast from the Past",
  "summary": "In the lobby of the Grand Palanhi Hotel, the smuggler-scholar Paul Nighman wakes from an accidental nap and notices a scruffy youth at the front desk asking after messages for someone named Shenner. The girl, Shenner Veery, disguised as a young man, flees the moment she recognizes him, but Paul follows her into the city and out to Starport Road, where she has gone to meet her friend Jessalyn Valios. Recognition turns explosive: Shenner attacks Paul, decking him and raging that he once stranded her on Tatooine after kissing her, while a baffled Jessalyn struggles to hold her back. Paul, stricken with guilt, finally explains the truth--that in a grief-soaked, drunken haze on the anniversary of losing a woman he once loved, he had mistaken Shenner for that lost love and lashed out, then convinced himself she would never want to see him again. The confession softens Shenner's fury into tears and, eventually, a wary truce sealed with a handshake. Paul resolves to leave Palanhi on the first available ship, and the two part on uneasy but genuine terms, Shenner passing along a warning about a dangerous redhead named Alora and a message of fondness for the droid Alx.",
